  "system": {
    "description": "<p>The standard drill-capable fighter craft of most TL4 polities, this model retains a spike drive instead of replacing it with a cheaper systems drive. This particular model is equipped with a reaper battery for dealing with small, lightly-armored civilian ships.</p><p><strong>Crew:</strong> 1/1 pilot. <strong>Cost:</strong> 305,000cr base price, 15,250cr six-month maintenance, 43,800cr yearly crew cost (1 pilot).</p><p><strong>NPC crew station convention:</strong> all five crew stations (Bridge, Gunnery, Engineering, Comms, Captain) use the check formula <code>2d6+Crew Skill</code> when no PC is assigned -- this ship's Crew Skill +2 gives <code>2d6+2</code> on every station. This convention applies to every ship in this compendium.</p>",
